## Chapter 8: E-bundles and paper bundles: length of documents


8.1 Unless the court has specifically directed otherwise, being satisfied that such direction is necessary to enable the proceedings to be disposed of justly, any of the following documents included in the bundle must be limited to no more than the number of pages (in the case of e-bundles) or the number of sheets of A4 paper (in the case of paper bundles) specified below:


Care plan: 10


Case summary: 6


Statement of issues: 2


Position statement: as provided in paragraphs 6.12(a) and 7.18(a)


Chronology: 10


List of essential reading: 1
